map_npcs.name: Raider Ruby
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Well, I guess it *is* happening.
You'll regret this!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, you want my shiny rocks?
Not happening!

map_npcs.name: Frightened Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: I need to get out of here!

map_npcs.name: Scared Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Please, go check deeper in the cave.
I think I'll stay here and keep watch, yeah...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
I... I think I heard screams from deeper in the cave.
Let's have a battle so that I don't have to hear them anymore!

map_npcs.name: Scout Jan
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: And here I thought I was supposed to be stealthy.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Ah! How'd you sneak up on me like that?

map_npcs.name: Explorer Dave
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ah, hello again!
These caves sure are vibrant, though it's odd...
It feels like the walls are practically alive here!
Perfect timing though, I've just finished a couple more pages of my notebook.
See ya around!

map_shops.greeting_dialog: Please insert Oochabux to despense product!
map_shops.greeting_dialogue: Welcome to my store. Buy whatever you need below!
